column5: Hey I was looking on the web and noticed Windsor Wholesale Baits, 2000 large night crawlers for $167 can. that is $1 can per doz. including shipping (great price) Has anyone have any experience with this company?
I live close by and buy a couple flats a year from them.
I bought two flats off them last year, I won't be buying off them again. They were not jumbo's by any means.
